{
  "stem": "868.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was a whole organization, not just a small institute.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The entire orphanage was surrounded by German troops.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they burst into our room where I and Willy was hidden.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "My brother, Harry, had in the meantime been transferred north to Treviso.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So there were just the-- just the two of us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They burst in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I understood German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I hear one of the two say to the other, only take the one that's over 18 years old.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Now, Willy had a false card.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I had a false-- false card.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But I was a year older and looking older than Willy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But Don Giovanni, when he made those cards, had the wisdom to make us a year younger.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So although, I was 18 at the time, the card said 17.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But now, they take me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they bring me down in the courtyard, lined up with another group of about, I would say eight or nine young men, who used to be orphans at the orphanage, but who since then had gone out into the world and come back now.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Which, I learned later, they were in the underground.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So now, I'm lined up against the wall with these other kids.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I'm saying to myself, now, I heard them say only those over 18.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, what if I make a fuss?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He will ask, how come you-- you-- you know about this business of 18?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It means I speak German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "How come you speak German, et cetera?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I figured, well, let's see first what they want to do with us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we're lined up against the wall and comes a group of soldiers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I told you, the entire area was surrounded, blocked, a group of two or three soldiers, one of them with a machine gun.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
